  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  rheumatic heart valve disease requiring selective aortic or double valve(aortic and
             mitral valve) replacement

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  infective endocarditis congenital valve disease previous cardiac surgery complicated
             with rereplace valve

          -  Renal dysfunction

          -  diabetes

          -  coronary artery disease

          -  hypertension

          -  peripheral vascular disease affecting the lower limb free of arteriovenous fistula

          -  receiving aspirin, corticosteroids, angiotensin-converting enzyme inhibitors or statin
             perioperatively
      </textblock>
